ke on this wise, That his seed should sojourn in a strange land; and that they should bring them into bondage, and entreat them evil four hundred years.","year":33},{"id":"recSwwy7k7E5ORpGu","ref":"Acts.7.7","text":"And the nation to whom they shall be in bondage will I judge, said God: and after that shall they come forth, and serve me in this place.","year":33},{"id":"recoHjw75mrm2EYPv","ref":"Acts.7.8","text":"And he gave him the covenant of circumcision: and so Abraham begat Isaac, and circumcised him the eighth day; and Isaac begat Jacob; and Jacob begat the twelve patriarchs.","year":33}]}
